chmod:

*who letters:
 * u user (me)
 * g group (all)
 * o others (not u or g)
 * a every single person

*permission letters:
 * r read
 * w write
 * x execute
 * X execute only if file is in a directory
 * s set user or group ID

*operations:
 * + add
 * - take away
 * = set exactly and remove all others

Grant read permission to everyone for foo.txt:

<verbatim>
  > chmod a+r foo.txt
</verbatim>
